	<article id="post-1033" class="post-1033 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-microcontrollers category-pic category-projects tag-arm tag-avr tag-fat tag-fat16 tag-file-system tag-pic tag-sd-card tag-tutorial">
				<header class="entry-header">
			
						<h1 class="entry-title">
				<a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/workshop-update-4-sd-card-and-fat16-implementation/" rel="bookmark">Workshop Update #4 &#8211; SD card and FAT16 implementation</a>
			</h1>
										<div class="comments-link">
					<a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/workshop-update-4-sd-card-and-fat16-implementation/#respond" title="Comment on Workshop Update #4 &#8211; SD card and FAT16 implementation"><span class="leave-reply">Leave a reply</span></a>				</div><!-- .comments-link -->
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>This is the 4th workshop update!</p>
<p>As you can see from the last two posts I am working on an SD card based data logger board. I have worked on getting the SD card communication protocol up and running and also have written my own FAT16 file system implementation (it&#8217;s pretty crude, though).<br />
 <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/workshop-update-4-sd-card-and-fat16-implementation/#more-1033" class="more-link">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
			This entry was posted in <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/category/microcontrollers/" title="View all posts in Microcontrollers" rel="category tag">Microcontrollers</a>, <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/category/pic/" title="View all posts in PIC" rel="category tag">PIC</a>, <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/category/projects/" title="View all posts in Projects" rel="category tag">Projects</a> and tagged <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/tag/arm/" rel="tag">ARM</a>, <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/tag/avr/" rel="tag">AVR</a>, <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/tag/fat/" rel="tag">FAT</a>, <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/tag/fat16/" rel="tag">FAT16</a>, <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/tag/file-system/" rel="tag">file system</a>, <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/tag/pic/" rel="tag">PIC</a>, <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/tag/sd-card/" rel="tag">SD card</a>, <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/tag/tutorial/" rel="tag">tutorial</a> on <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/workshop-update-4-sd-card-and-fat16-implementation/" title="11:06 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-03-25T11:06:04+00:00">March 25, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://eliaselectronics.com/author/elia/" title="View all posts by Elia" rel="author">Elia</a></span></span>.								</footer><!-- .entry-meta -->
