	<article id="post-1029" class="post-1029 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-guides category-microcontrollers category-projects tag-data-logger tag-fat16 tag-project tag-tutorial">
				<header class="entry-header">
			
						<h1 class="entry-title">
				<a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/a-look-at-the-fat16-filesystem/" rel="bookmark">A look at the FAT16 filesystem</a>
			</h1>
										<div class="comments-link">
					<a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/a-look-at-the-fat16-filesystem/#respond" title="Comment on A look at the FAT16 filesystem"><span class="leave-reply">Leave a reply</span></a>				</div><!-- .comments-link -->
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>As you might know I am working on an SD datalogger project. In order to write data to the SD card and directly access it from the computer I need to implement FAT16 filesystem handling.<br />
I haven&#8217;t found any video about how exactly FAT works so I have made a video myself.<br />
Enjoy!<br />
<iframe width="640" height="360" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/VekPA14ffBU" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
			This entry was posted in <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/category/guides/" title="View all posts in Guides" rel="category tag">Guides</a>, <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/category/microcontrollers/" title="View all posts in Microcontrollers" rel="category tag">Microcontrollers</a>, <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/category/projects/" title="View all posts in Projects" rel="category tag">Projects</a> and tagged <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/tag/data-logger/" rel="tag">data logger</a>, <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/tag/fat16/" rel="tag">FAT16</a>, <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/tag/project/" rel="tag">project</a>, <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/tag/tutorial/" rel="tag">tutorial</a> on <a href="http://eliaselectronics.com/a-look-at-the-fat16-filesystem/" title="1:10 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-03-23T13:10:03+00:00">March 23, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://eliaselectronics.com/author/elia/" title="View all posts by Elia" rel="author">Elia</a></span></span>.								</footer><!-- .entry-meta -->
